out there for free on the web.

00:39:12.970 --> 00:39:15.400
And he said, yeah, I know.

00:39:15.400 --> 00:39:16.640
OK!

00:39:16.640 --> 00:39:18.370
And so, we've been
about six months

00:39:18.370 --> 00:39:20.890
putting the book together.

00:39:20.890 --> 00:39:26.590
And it's really exciting.

00:39:26.590 --> 00:39:28.060
And I'm still writing.

